romexpander 0.4
===============

``romexpander`` can be run exactly like ROM Expander Pro,
otherwise behaviour is overridden by CLI arguments.

Installation::

    pip install romexpander

Usage::

    romexpander [options] [INPUT]
    romexpander [-h | --help]
    romexpander [-v | --version]

Arguments:
    INPUT                   optional input ROM file.

Options:
    -v, --version           show version info.
    -h, --help              show this message.
    -o, --output target     specify an output file.
    -t, --txt cfg           specify a config file.
